Subject: [PATCH 238/587] config: Add bcm2835-codec to Pi defconfigs.

Adds the V4L2 M2M codec driver to the config.

Signed-off-by: Dave Stevenson <dave.stevenson@raspberrypi.org>
---
 arch/arm/configs/bcm2709_defconfig | 1 +
 arch/arm/configs/bcmrpi_defconfig  | 1 +
 2 files changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/bcm2709_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/bcm2709_defconfig
index a736e23f4726..dbff5f6d1540 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/bcm2709_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/bcm2709_defconfig
@@ -1225,6 +1225,7 @@ CONFIG_FB_TFT_FBTFT_DEVICE=m
 CONFIG_BCM2835_VCHIQ=y
 CONFIG_SND_BCM2835=m
 CONFIG_VIDEO_BCM2835=m
+CONFIG_VIDEO_CODEC_BCM2835=m
 CONFIG_MAILBOX=y
 CONFIG_BCM2835_MBOX=y
 # CONFIG_IOMMU_SUPPORT is not set
diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/bcmrpi_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/bcmrpi_defconfig
index 9f29ce332a7f..c5e2db692e4f 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/bcmrpi_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/bcmrpi_defconfig
@@ -1217,6 +1217,7 @@ CONFIG_FB_TFT_FBTFT_DEVICE=m
 CONFIG_BCM2835_VCHIQ=y
 CONFIG_SND_BCM2835=m
 CONFIG_VIDEO_BCM2835=m
+CONFIG_VIDEO_CODEC_BCM2835=m
 CONFIG_MAILBOX=y
 CONFIG_BCM2835_MBOX=y
 # CONFIG_IOMMU_SUPPORT is not set
